title: Big stops: Big House, Death Valley, A&M, NW, South Bend
text: > Top News Big stops: Big House, Death Valley, A&M, NW, South Bend FILE - In this Oct. 10, 2015, file photo, Utah quarterback Travis Wilson (7) looking downfield in the second half during an NCAA college football game against California, in Salt Lake City. The play of Wilson was a huge reason the Utes shot up the rankings and now sit at No. 4. The play of Wilson is also the reason why there are questions about the Utes' legitimacy. (AP Photo/Rick Bowmer, File)
